Story 2: Getting Related Searches
- After loggin in and searching the location, you get all the relevant posts that relates to your search.
- Once you finished scrolling through all the relevant posts, we suggest the user to click a button to generate related posts.
- Here are the following steps taken to get the related results:
    1. the relevant results' usernames 
    2. Collect all the locations they've visited 
    3. Return the most common location between all these users' posts
    OR
    1. Return other people's serches from previous logins that are close to the location the current user entered
- View all the related posts in the same manner as the relevant posts.
- Connect with whoever visited awesome places. 
